con:interface.name: KEMP LoadMaster API.
con:interface.con:description:
## KEMP LoadMaster ADC Public API
Kemp’s Virtual LoadMaster is a fully featured load balancer and application delivery controller (ADC) that supports all the major application workloads with easy-to-use templates. It offers key features such as SSL offload along with advanced authentication and traffic delivery options.
Virtual LoadMaster (VLM) instances can be deployed on all major hypervisors and on leading public cloud services with a consistent set of features regardless of where deployed. Consistency across a wide range of platforms greatly simplifies cloud migration and hybrid cloud deployments with seamless migration and reduced management complexity.
__This API uses live LoadMaster end-points delivered via the `AWS API Gateway`__
--- ![diagram](https://media.publit.io/file/lm-aws.png)
---
## LoadMaster API Environment AWS VM | URL - | - AWS Gateway | [https://loadmaster.mwhigging.net](https://loadmaster.mwhigging.net) LoadMaster01 | [https://loadmaster01.mwhiggins.net](https://loadmaster01.mwhiggins.net) LoadMaster02 | https://loadmaster01.mwhiggins.net
---
## Release History: date | user | comments - | - | - 07/05/2020 | m.higgins | initial coding 21/05/2020 | m.higgins | added local Server tags 09/06/2020 | m.higgins | implemented 2 domains 10/11/2020 | m.higgins | now require "default" response 04/12/2020 | m.higgins | added end-point /access/listcert
---
